      "Text": "An update for golang is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS",
      "Title": "Summary",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": ".\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nThe net/http package improperly accepts a bare LF as a line terminator in chunked data chunk-size lines. This can permit request smuggling if a net/http server is used in conjunction with a server that incorrectly accepts a bare LF as part of a chunk-ext.(CVE-2025-22871)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
